'''Amy Allen''' (born [[October 24]], [[1976]]<ref name="This Week Hype" />) is an [[Wikipedia:America|American]] actress best known for her role as [[Twi'lek]] [[Jedi]] [[Aayla Secura]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']].

==Biography==
Aside from portraying [[Jedi Knight]] [[Aayla Secura]], she also portrayed three extras in the [[Outlander Club]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]. Namely, within the [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] continuity, these were identified as the [[Nalle triplets]]: [[Mya Nalle|Mya]], [[Yma Nalle|Yma]], and [[Lela Nalle Mayn|Lela Mayn]] (all three names are anagrams of the actress's name). Additionally, she played a [[Twi'lek]] [[senatorial aide]] [[Pampy]] in the [[Star Wars home video releases|DVD version]] of [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']], replacing the [[Human]] [[aide]]s of [[Senator]] [[Orn Free Taa]].

